Description: |
  yt-down is a modern command-line tool for downloading YouTube videos
  and converting them to MP3 format. It supports:
  .
   * Download of individual videos and complete playlists
   * Parallel processing for faster downloads
   * Configurable audio quality and output formats
   * Automatic ID3 metadata tagging
   * Progress bars and detailed logging
   * Robust error handling and recovery
  .
  The tool is designed for personal use and educational purposes.
  Please respect copyright laws and YouTube's terms of service.
